NK080(wu)031:1: // dpe chung rang gnas zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK080(wu)031:2: bcom ldan 'das ye shes rang gnas rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK080(wu)031:5: dngos dang bar ma rnam sbyang phyir //
NK080(wu)031:6: dpe chung rang gnas bshad par bya //
NK080(wu)031:7: rgyu dang rang bzhin rgyud nyid dang //
NK080(wu)031:8: rang bzhin nang gi dkyil 'khor dang //
NK080(wu)031:9: 'pho tshul bar ma'i mtshan nyid dang //
NK080(wu)031:10: las bsnyen gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor gsum //
NK080(wu)031:11: de dag ting 'dzin las rim dang //
NK080(wu)031:12: rang gnas sbyang ba'i rim pa dang //
NK080(wu)031:13: bdag nyid 'da' ba'i man ngag dang //
NK080(wu)031:14: mthar gnas tshul gyi tha snyad bcu //
NK080(wu)031:15: rang gnas rmongs pa'i don phyir dbye //
NK080(wu)031:16: dang po rnam gnyis de la'ang gnyis //
NK080(wu)031:17: bder gshegs snying po rang rig la //
NK080(wu)031:18: ma rig bdag lta mtshungs pa'i rgyu //
NK080(wu)031:19: kun brtags ma rig nyon mongs la //
NK080(wu)031:20: lhan cig byed rgyu rgyu yi rgyu //
NK080(wu)031:21: gnyis pa rkyen gyi rnam par 'dod //
NK080(wu)031:22: mtshams sbyor rnam shes zhen bcas pa //
NK080(wu)031:23: rlung gi rkyen gyis 'ongs mtshungs rgyu //
NK080(wu)031:24: rten sems lan pa khrag dang bcas //
NK080(wu)031:25: pho mo 'dod bsnol sems kyis 'jug /len rten 'byung ba nges ldan pas //
NK080(wu)031:26: thal ba 'bru mar sha rul ltar //
NK080(wu)031:28: sum cu rtsa brgyad phrag bdun rlung //
NK080(wu)031:29: lhan cig byed rgyu rkyen du 'dod //
NK080(wu)031:30: las rlung dang po zho chags tshul //
NK080(wu)031:31: kun sdud ma yi rtsib ma 'bud //
NK080(wu)031:32: cung zad sra bar 'gyur ba yis //
NK080(wu)031:33: mdzod ces bya bas zlum par byed //
NK080(wu)031:34: rab 'byed mkhregs pas mchig gu lta //
NK080(wu)031:35: yang dag sdud pas yan lag gi /rtsa ba lnga po 'byung bar 'gyur //
NK080(wu)031:37: 'khyil byed de bzhin lnga rdzogs byed //
NK080(wu)031:38: bzlog bsgyur byed pas nyid lag rdzogs //
NK080(wu)031:39: rnam par 'byed pas bug dgu dod //
NK080(wu)031:40: sra byed kun nas sgo mnyam pas //
NK080(wu)031:41: sra zhing rkyal pa lta bur gyur //
NK080(wu)031:42: rdo rje bug sbyongs kha sna nas //
NK080(wu)031:43: khrag snag chu 'byung dbang po bzlog /yon po'i sgos ni rang grol 'byung //
NK080(wu)031:44: zhor 'byung sdu rgyus shes pa'i las //
NK080(wu)031:45: rus pa'i tshigs dang nad rnams ldan //
NK080(wu)031:46: bkres skom byed pas de sems skye //
NK080(wu)031:47: mas zos lte bar 'dzin cing phan //
NK080(wu)031:48: skud pa'i sgo ni chu rgyus g.yo //
NK080(wu)031:50: phyogs bzhir lnga lnga gcig la'ang brgyad //
NK080(wu)031:51: nying lag phyogs gcig nyi khri la //
NK080(wu)031:52: mdun rgyab sa ga stobs zhes bya //
NK080(wu)031:53: g.yas g.yon mthur ldan brtan pa'o //
NK080(wu)031:54: de dag nyid lag gcig nas bdun //
NK080(wu)031:55: dag gi bar de ba spur 'brel //
NK080(wu)031:56: kha dog dkar dmar ser sngo ldan //
NK080(wu)031:57: mdud rtsi dbang po snying mig 'byed //
NK080(wu)031:58: dbugs rgyu dbang po rnams kyang rdzogs //
NK080(wu)031:59: 'bri gtong dbang po dang bar byed //
NK080(wu)031:60: brtan 'gyur dbang po las mthu ldan //
NK080(wu)031:61: las byed dbang po gsum rdzogs byed //
NK080(wu)031:62: shin tu sra bar rus pa brtan //
NK080(wu)031:63: yang dag bskyed pas sha rnams bskyed //
NK080(wu)031:64: kun tu rgyal bas khrag rnams 'byung //
NK080(wu)031:65: yongs dag 'dzin pas lpags pa g.yogs //
NK080(wu)031:66: sprin 'dzin de nyid mdog ldan byed //
NK080(wu)031:67: grong khyer 'dzin pas khrag mdang byed //
NK080(wu)031:68: skye ba mngon grub spu rnams dang //
NK080(wu)031:69: chu rgyu sen mo 'brel bar byed //
NK080(wu)031:70: phan yon chen pos las bzhin du //
NK080(wu)031:71: mdzes dang che chung gsal bar byed //
NK080(wu)031:73: me tog 'phreng bas kha dog sgyur //
NK080(wu)031:74: lcags sgos spu dang sen mo 'phel //
NK080(wu)031:75: bdun phrag lnga po yangs byed kyis //
NK080(wu)031:78: ldang bas phyin ci ma log pa'i //
NK080(wu)031:80: de dag rang bzhin gsang ba'i las //
NK080(wu)031:81: chags srog rang bzhin bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK080(wu)031:82: shin tu gsal bar byed par 'gyur //
NK080(wu)031:83: thogs med rkyen gyis mgo lus bsgyur //
NK080(wu)031:84: rang bzhin sems dpa' lhums nas 'byung //
NK080(wu)031:85: rang bzhin ye shes rdo rje'i phyir //
NK080(wu)031:86: rdo rje'i phung po zhes gsungs so //
NK080(wu)031:87: rang bzhin gnas rgyud rnam pa gnyis //
NK080(wu)031:88: sems ni rang rig ye shes te //
NK080(wu)031:89: ma bcos rgyun gyi skad cig ma //
NK080(wu)031:90: de yis ma byas gang yang med //
NK080(wu)031:91: rang rig mun 'khor bslad pa ni //
NK080(wu)031:94: mi mthun bde sdug myong 'gyur ba'i //
NK080(wu)031:95: dbang po yul du snang ba kun //
NK080(wu)031:96: rang rgyud yod pa ma yin te //
NK080(wu)031:97: kun gzhi rnam par shes pa nyid //
NK080(wu)031:98: dngos po sna tshogs bar snang bas //
NK080(wu)031:99: gnyis snang chos kun rnam rtog bshad //
NK080(wu)031:100: rnam rtog nyid na ye shes te //
NK080(wu)031:101: ma skyes ye shes brjod du med //
NK080(wu)031:102: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /sems nyid las gzhan med pa'i phyir //
NK080(wu)031:103: 'di ltar snang ba thams cad kun //
NK080(wu)031:104: brdos pa can gyi chos min te //
NK080(wu)031:105: rtog med rang rig 'od gsal ba'i //
NK080(wu)031:106: shes pa 'ba' zhig khog na'i phyir //
NK080(wu)031:107: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs pa'i //
NK080(wu)031:108: snang ba gnyis na ngo bo med //
NK080(wu)031:109: de nyid chos sku chen por gsungs //
NK080(wu)031:110: rnam dag rang bzhin rgyud nyid la //
NK080(wu)031:111: bsgo dang bsgo bar bya ba yi //
NK080(wu)031:112: mtshan ma'i nyes skyon ngang gis med //
NK080(wu)031:113: gnas dang 'byung ba ma lus kun //
NK080(wu)031:114: rang nyid ye shes gzugs su skye //
NK080(wu)031:115: sku dang ye shes bsam mi khyab //
NK080(wu)031:116: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK080(wu)031:117: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK080(wu)031:118: sa chu spyan dang m+aa ma ki //
NK080(wu)031:119: me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma ste /
NK080(wu)031:120: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma /
NK080(wu)031:121: skye mched khams rnams mang po kun /
NK080(wu)031:122: sems dpa' sems ma'i dkyil 'khor yin /
NK080(wu)031:123: gsang yul dbang po rnam shes reg /ma lus 'joms phyir khro mor gsungs /
NK080(wu)031:124: rtag sogs mtshan ma las skye'i phyir //
NK080(wu)031:125: lum ste las kyi mi gnas bshad //
NK080(wu)031:126: yid chos bzang po bzang mo'i mkha' //so drug las byung bde ba'i dus //
NK080(wu)031:127: chags sogs yang dag nyon mongs drug /ye shes drug gis sa bon drug /
NK080(wu)031:128: 'dul phyir sprul sku zhes su gsungs //
NK080(wu)031:129: sku dang gsung thugs yon tan las //
NK080(wu)031:130: nyi shu rtsa lngar rang bzhin gnas //
NK080(wu)031:131: chos nyid ye shes yon tan ni //
NK080(wu)031:132: ting 'dzin gsum gyi ngo bo yin //
NK080(wu)031:133: de stengs dngas ma'i thig le ni //
NK080(wu)031:134: bsnyen sgrub bzhi ru shes par bya //
NK080(wu)031:135: de dbyings las bzhi'i dkyil 'khor te //
NK080(wu)031:136: bzhi brgyad rtsa ni 'khor lo gsungs //
NK080(wu)031:137: gsang ba'i skabs las shes par bya //
NK080(wu)031:138: bdes gang bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rtsa //
NK080(wu)031:139: sa bon sku ste yi ge gsung //
NK080(wu)031:140: bde thugs rdo rje sku gsung ldan //
NK080(wu)031:142: gcig kyang khams kyi bde ba lnga //
NK080(wu)031:143: ye shes chen po'i ros gang bas //
NK080(wu)031:144: ma lus 'joms pas rgyas btab po //
NK080(wu)031:145: 'bru bzhi nges par ldan pa'i tshe //
NK080(wu)031:146: sgra dbyangs gsung gi bstan pa rnams //
NK080(wu)031:147: nges par ston phyir bzhi ru 'dod //
NK080(wu)031:148: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NK080(wu)031:149: de ni lung gi tshad mar bshad //
NK080(wu)031:150: tshad bzhi phob pa'i don yin te //
NK080(wu)031:151: dag pa rnam gsum la gnas shing //
NK080(wu)031:153: 'gro ba kun la rang bzhin gnas //
NK080(wu)031:154: rang bzhin mngon du byed rgyud ni //
NK080(wu)031:155: ngo bo dang ni rkyen nyid do //
NK080(wu)031:156: 'jig ldang las sogs byang sems lnga //
NK080(wu)031:157: nges par skye ba ngo bo yin //
NK080(wu)031:158: thabs dang shes rab ma ning rgyud //
NK080(wu)031:159: bstan pa'i yig lam rkyen du gsungs //
NK080(wu)031:160: khong nas gas spas don 'byin pa //
NK080(wu)031:161: ston pa rdo rje'i thugs la gnas //
NK080(wu)031:162: rang bzhin gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK080(wu)031:163: dkyil 'khor snying po gser sgrom la //
NK080(wu)031:164: chos nyid ye shes yon tan dang //
NK080(wu)031:165: rang rgyud bzhi la yan lag brgyad //
NK080(wu)031:166: 'od bzhi la gnas rnam shes bzhi //
NK080(wu)031:167: sgo lnga rtag min zhor la bshad //
NK080(wu)031:168: sa bon zung gsum gnyid dang bcas //
NK080(wu)031:169: 'od la snod bcud tshul du gnas //
NK080(wu)031:170: chos nyid lha min dud 'gro zlum //
NK080(wu)031:171: kun gzhi gyi snying po can //
NK080(wu)031:172: ye shes lha mi grub bzhi yid //
NK080(wu)031:173: snying po h+aum ni bde gshegs thugs //
NK080(wu)031:174: yon tan dmyal ba yi dwags //
NK080(wu)031:175: zla kham gsung gi rang bzhin yin //
NK080(wu)031:176: dmar nag gdog la gshol dbyibs //
NK080(wu)031:177: de ni blo rmugs snod yin no //
NK080(wu)031:178: shes pa gsum la snyoms par bgegs //
NK080(wu)031:179: drag po nyid du'ang 'dod pa yin //
NK080(wu)031:180: de dbus snying po ye shes sku //
NK080(wu)031:181: dar skud mtshal khu gser gyi rlangs //
NK080(wu)031:182: nyi ma'i me long ngad dag ni //
NK080(wu)031:184: bde ba'i dngas ma nam mkha'i khams //
NK080(wu)031:185: 'byung ba shes rab rigs kyi yum //
NK080(wu)031:186: chen po rigs kyi de bzhin gshegs //
NK080(wu)031:187: thabs dang shes rab las nyid kyis //
NK080(wu)031:188: dkyil 'khor kun kyang gsal bar byed //
NK080(wu)031:190: thams cad nam mkha'ara byed pa'i phyir //
NK080(wu)031:191: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dkyil 'khor mchog /las can kun la yod par bshad //
NK080(wu)031:192: sgrub pa'i gzhi ru 'di shes bya //
NK080(wu)031:193: 'khrul dbang mi gnas tha snyad du //
NK080(wu)031:194: rnam shes 'pho bar gsungs pa ni //
NK080(wu)031:195: nyi 'od sa bon skyur sgra bzhin //
NK080(wu)031:196: rgyu las 'bras bu gzhan min gyi //
NK080(wu)031:198: rdul cha tsam yang med par gsungs //
NK080(wu)031:199: sa chu me rlung bzhi yi rlung //
NK080(wu)031:200: sum mdo snying lkog lte ba la //
NK080(wu)031:201: rim gnas khams gsum rten yin te //
NK080(wu)031:202: las rgyud zad pa'i rkyen dag gis //
NK080(wu)031:203: srog dbang yan lag nyams pas na //
NK080(wu)031:204: tshogs drug par thim gsal mi 'gyur //
NK080(wu)031:205: sa dag chur zhugs lus nyams med //
NK080(wu)031:206: de nyid mer zhugs bu ga bskams //
NK080(wu)031:208: rlung ni snying po thig le ste //
NK080(wu)031:209: rngub cing tha mar thon par 'gyur //
NK080(wu)031:210: thig le me long dbugs bzhin du //
NK080(wu)031:211: 'gro don spyi yi yul nub ste //
NK080(wu)031:212: dmigs pa med pa'i rjes thob las //
NK080(wu)031:213: dpe bzhin tshul gyi bar ma 'am //
NK080(wu)031:214: lus dang phyi ma'i spyod yul snang //
NK080(wu)031:215: de phyir 'pho ba tha snyad du //
NK080(wu)031:216: btags pa'i yon par shes par bya //
NK080(wu)031:217: bar ma'i byang chub sems dpa' ni //
NK080(wu)031:218: rnam rtog 'byung ba'i lus spangs nas //
NK080(wu)031:219: dngas ma las byung yid kyi lus //
NK080(wu)031:220: phyis 'byung dbang po yan lag rdzogs //
NK080(wu)031:221: las kyi rdzu 'phrul shugs dang ldan //
NK080(wu)031:222: sgyu ma lta bu lus dag gis //
NK080(wu)031:223: thogs pa med par kun la 'jug /dpag tshad bye ba brgya stong yang //
NK080(wu)031:225: 'dod khams snod bcud ma lus pa //
NK080(wu)031:226: lha mig dag pas mthong bar 'gyur //
NK080(wu)031:227: 'gro ba'i lam dag nges par shes //
NK080(wu)031:228: re dang dogs pa cung zad nyung //
NK080(wu)031:229: tshe ni zhag bdun 'gyur du gsungs //
NK080(wu)031:230: 'chi kha'i man ngag rab shes pas //
NK080(wu)031:232: ma skyes rang bzhin ye shes las //
NK080(wu)031:233: e ram khams gsum e dkyil 'khor //
NK080(wu)031:234: me dpung 'bar ba'i klong yangs su //
NK080(wu)031:235: rang rig ye shes rang snang ba //
NK080(wu)031:237: ma lus khrag 'thung rdo rje'i rigs //
NK080(wu)031:238: mthing nag 'jigs pa'i mtshon cha can //
NK080(wu)031:239: gcer bu rngams tshul til gang sbyar //
NK080(wu)031:240: khros pas sngangs langs khams gsum dkrugs //
NK080(wu)031:241: bsgrub bya dmigs su len par bsgom //
NK080(wu)031:242: dur khrod ras kyi dkyil 'khor la //
NK080(wu)031:243: khrag 'thung drug cu rtsa drug rnams //
NK080(wu)031:244: rim pa gsum du brtsegs pa ni //
NK080(wu)031:245: byin rlabs dbang gi mdzes pa yi //
NK080(wu)031:246: rngam tshul gzi byin ldan par sgom //
NK080(wu)031:247: ye shes spyan drangs mchod gsum sbyor //
NK080(wu)031:248: bzlas pa srog dang ldan par bya //
NK080(wu)031:249: thugs rje'i dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK080(wu)031:250: rang bzhin yid kyis dmigs byas te //
NK080(wu)031:251: gcig dang du ma med tshul gyis //
NK080(wu)031:252: sangs rgyas kun gyi ngo bo brtag /bsdu ba'i sbyor bas kun bsdus te //
NK080(wu)031:253: byin rlabs bstang par gsol bar bya //
NK080(wu)031:254: bsgrub bya khrus byas dri dang ldan //
NK080(wu)031:255: nges par shar sgo nyid du gzung //
NK080(wu)031:256: dkyil 'khor dang po gsal byas la //
NK080(wu)031:257: sprul pas mtshams bcad bum pa gzung //
NK080(wu)031:258: bshad pa bzhin du bsgrub bya da gug /nges par gzugs la phob ste bcings //
NK080(wu)031:261: 'dus pas bsgrub bya gnas sbyangs nas //
NK080(wu)031:262: rtog tshogs dkyil 'khor nyid du brlab //
NK080(wu)031:263: slob bu sbyang ba'i rim par gsungs //
NK080(wu)031:264: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor sgo phye nas //
NK080(wu)031:265: phyag rgya skor te gsal btab dang //
NK080(wu)031:266: sgrib sbyangs rang gi lhar bskyed la //
NK080(wu)031:267: 'khor lo'i phyag rgyas bsrung bar bya //
NK080(wu)031:268: ta krita la sogs nges sbyor ba'i //
NK080(wu)031:269: sngags dang yungs dkar sprul pa yis //
NK080(wu)031:270: nges grogs rtse mo mkha' la bzhag /de dag 'od zer mang po yi //
NK080(wu)031:271: nyon mongs mun pa dag byas nas //
NK080(wu)031:272: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor mthong bar bya //
NK080(wu)031:273: rigs drug sbyor ba'i 'od zer gyis //
NK080(wu)031:274: sa bon rnam par drug sbyangs te //
NK080(wu)031:275: zung gsum 'od gyi gong bu gsum //
NK080(wu)031:276: rnam mthar sku gsum yig gsum gyis //
NK080(wu)031:277: kha dog rang rgyud bzhin du 'gyur //
NK080(wu)031:278: 'od kyi sngon bzhin byin brlabs bstim //
NK080(wu)031:279: rnam shes thugs te yig ge gsung //
NK080(wu)031:280: 'od ni sku yi rang bzhin las //
NK080(wu)031:281: dpa' sgeg byams pa gar byed rgyal //
NK080(wu)031:282: gsal ma chos nyid bdag nyid ma //
NK080(wu)031:283: sku gsung dgu phrug ldan pa yis //
NK080(wu)031:284: thabs dang shes rab 'byor bar skyed //
NK080(wu)031:285: rnam thar dbu dang ye shes phyag /khams gsum sku gsung thugs rgyas btab //
NK080(wu)031:286: bcu gnyis pa la nges par phyin //
NK080(wu)031:287: byang chub sems kyis dbang skur te //
NK080(wu)031:288: rdo rje'i thugs la dbur byung ba //
NK080(wu)031:289: che mchog rgyun gyi dbang skur bas //
NK080(wu)031:291: thabs dang shes rab ldan sgyur te //
NK080(wu)031:293: bde gshegs rgyun gyis byin brlabs pas //
NK080(wu)031:294: che mchog dbang mchog dpal mchog gsum //
NK080(wu)031:295: thabs dang shes rab 'khril bar bsgom //
NK080(wu)031:296: dbang mchog rol pa sems 'di nyid //
NK080(wu)031:297: che mchog mkha' la bsdu bar bya //
NK080(wu)031:298: de nyid dpal mchog la zhugs te //
NK080(wu)031:299: dpal mchog rang gi gsang lam nas //
NK080(wu)031:300: dwangs ma'i ye shes snying por thim //
NK080(wu)031:301: gzhi yi sku gsung thugs nyid kyang //
NK080(wu)031:302: de bzhin 'dus pa nyid du bya //
NK080(wu)031:303: brgya rtsa brgyad kyi snying po yis //
NK080(wu)031:304: dus bzhi'i bde ba mchog du bsdu //
NK080(wu)031:305: gtsug gi lam nas thig ler zhugs //
NK080(wu)031:306: mi shigs ye shes thig le ni //
NK080(wu)031:307: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje bdag /gcig dang du ma rnam spangs ba //
NK080(wu)031:308: sna tshogs snang la mtshon du med //
NK080(wu)031:309: rang dbang gyur pa'i h+aum rings las //
NK080(wu)031:310: sems dpa'i rdo rje mtshon gang pa //
NK080(wu)031:311: dbu la ye shes sems dpa'i bzhugs //
NK080(wu)031:313: gtsug byung thugs rje dbang thob nas //
NK080(wu)031:314: thabs dang shes rab ldan gyur pas //
NK080(wu)031:315: stong phrag gcig gi rtsa bcud rnams //
NK080(wu)031:316: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK080(wu)031:317: mngon byung rigs kyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK080(wu)031:318: nam mkha'i khams kyang de bzhin no //
NK080(wu)031:319: sh+r+ai ma h+aa su kha badz+ra h+aum hoh h+aum /
NK080(wu)031:320: ma bgrod yid kyis byon pa'i gnas mchog gdal ba la //
NK080(wu)031:321: yid bzhin rin chen 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK080(wu)031:322: dus gsum 'gyur ba med pa'i gdan stengs na //
NK080(wu)031:323: rtag pa chen po mchog gi sku bzhugs pa //
NK080(wu)031:324: mnyam rdzogs dpe las 'das pa'i rgyan mnga' zhing //
NK080(wu)031:325: yid bzhin rin chen gter la bde spyod pa //
NK080(wu)031:326: bde ba chen po dag la rtag spyod pa //
NK080(wu)031:327: rtag pa chen po longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK080(wu)031:328: rdzogs chen 'gyur med g.yung drung gdab ba'i ngang //
NK080(wu)031:329: bde chen dbyings kyi yum dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NK080(wu)031:330: ting 'dzin bdud rtsi'i thugs ni sangs rgyas yangs kyi bcud //
NK080(wu)031:331: rnam dag ye shes spyan gyis mun nag gsal //
NK080(wu)031:332: ye shes sgron ma'i thugs kyis bag chags bsregs //
NK080(wu)031:333: rdo rje spu gri tshems kyis dug gsum bcad //
NK080(wu)031:334: rngams chen h+aum nyid ring pos khro chen brtul //
NK080(wu)031:335: thugs dam mu la dz+wa las dmyal khams bsregs //
NK080(wu)031:336: ye shes rol pas rgyud drug gnas nas sgrol //
NK080(wu)031:337: srid gsum zhal gyis rgyal sras spro ba skyed //
NK080(wu)031:338: ye shes byang sems sangs rgyas yongs kyis dpal //
NK080(wu)031:339: dpal chen bla med khro rgyal 'bum gyi rje //
NK080(wu)031:340: kun bzang rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs te //
NK080(wu)031:341: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi lha phud yin //
NK080(wu)031:342: ma lus 'don pa'i dpal du nges par mdzod //
NK080(wu)031:343: spyod yul 'gyur ba mthong ba na //
NK080(wu)031:344: gsang ba'i gnas su nyon mongs kyis //
NK080(wu)031:345: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal ba la //
NK080(wu)031:346: kun gzhi ye shes snying po yi //
NK080(wu)031:347: 'od kyis khams gsum sbyangs bsdus te //
NK080(wu)031:348: mtshon gang 'od du gsal ba las //
NK080(wu)031:349: dkar po h+aum gnas rnam shes so //
NK080(wu)031:350: de dag sku gsung thugs dag ste //
NK080(wu)031:351: shin tu 'dris pa nyid du bya //
NK080(wu)031:352: rlung rtseg bcud g.yo'i mtshan mthong nas //
NK080(wu)031:353: ring po h+aum nyid na sa nas //
NK080(wu)031:354: de bzhin zla ba'am shes par bya //
NK080(wu)031:355: 'od rlung gsang ba'i lam zhugs te //
NK080(wu)031:356: phyir 'byung phyogs bcur khyab gdal bas //
NK080(wu)031:357: khams gsum bdag phyir mtha' dbus dang //
NK080(wu)031:358: phyi nang yul sems bral ba'i don //
NK080(wu)031:359: dran pas las kyi rgyun bcad pas //
NK080(wu)031:360: rang gnas mthong bar 'gyur ba yin //
NK080(wu)031:361: gsang ba'i zhabs kyis rnam pa ni //
NK080(wu)031:362: gnyis kyang rnam shes yig 'dus te //
NK080(wu)031:363: lce rtse rkan la sbyar byas nas //
NK080(wu)031:364: h+aum ring bla med he rur gyur //
NK080(wu)031:365: sna tshogs mdog ldan rgyan rdzogs pa //
NK080(wu)031:366: h+aum brjod na sa'i lam phyung ste //
NK080(wu)031:369: theg mchog gsang mtha' mngon byas pa //
NK080(wu)031:370: gzhi bzhin ma lus bdag nyid phyir //
NK080(wu)031:371: rgya bral gcig dang du ma spangs //
NK080(wu)031:373: ro myong bdag nyid rnam rtog bral //
NK080(wu)031:374: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK080(wu)031:375: thugs rje chen pos ma lus mkhyen //
NK080(wu)031:376: sku dang gsung thugs yon tan las //
NK080(wu)031:377: khyab dang bde dang rtag dbang bsgyur //
NK080(wu)031:378: rkyen gyis skye 'jig med pa'i phyir //
NK080(wu)031:379: rtag chen rdo rje'i sku zhes bya /
NK080(wu)031:380: rang bzhin gnas rgyud ye shes phyag rgya bsam yas mngon sum yul bral rang gnas la /
NK080(wu)031:381: 'khrul dang rnam pa rang rgyud log par rtog gsum las rkyen rab rib zhen snang ba /
NK080(wu)031:382: thabs mkhas spyan mnga' rgyud bzhi sgro bral rgyud gsum thur mas gsal phyir gab gsungs pa //
NK080(wu)031:383: dpyod yid gams nyams rna rgyud nyams shar gsal byas 'das dang da ltar 'ang rig mig thob shog //
NK080(wu)031:384: slob dpon chen po dur khrod bde ba gsal mdzad
NK080(wu)031:385: kyis mdzad pa dpe chung rang gnas zhes bya ba
